  Version bump.

  12 Mar 2013; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -kramdown-0.13.8.ebuild,
  -kramdown-0.14.0.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

*kramdown-0.14.1 (01 Dec 2012)

