*kramdown-0.13.5-r1 (11 Mar 2012)

  11 Mar 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +kramdown-0.13.5-r1.ebuild:
  Add latex USE flag to pull in the proper dependencies for latex support. Also
  fix tests when not all latex dependencies are installed.

