*kramdown-0.13.4 (18 Dec 2011)

  18 Dec 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +kramdown-0.13.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add ruby19. Require new enough version of coderay for tests.
  It's optional but we need at least this version.

  19 Jun 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> kramdown-0.13.3.ebuild:
  Only generate docs when USE=doc. Fixes bug 372189, thanks to Kai Dietrich for
  the proposed fix.

  19 Jun 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -kramdown-0.13.2.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

